Planck {CMB} and Λ{CDM} is 6.6 ± 1.5 km s-1
Mpc-1 or 4.4σ (P = 99.999\% for Gaussian errors)
in significance, raising the discrepancy beyond a plausible level of
chance. We summarize independent tests showing that this discrepancy is
