ics that could be expected to vary between optical and {NIR} wavelengths, like dust extinction. We anticipate further improvements in H{\textless}{SUB}{\textgreater}0{\textless}/{SUB}{\textgreater} with a larger calibrator sample of {SNe} Ia with Cepheid distances, more Hubble flow {SNe} Ia with {NIR} light curves, and better use of the full {NIR} photometric data set beyond simply the peak J-band magnitude.},
